{"title":"轻量应用服务器部署SpringBoot项目","uid":"e8d2f85354ae6e19f9a309efbfdecf4c","slug":"服务器/轻量应用服务器部署SpringBoot项目","date":"2022-02-09T15:59:34.000Z","updated":"2022-03-14T14:17:25.230Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/服务器/轻量应用服务器部署SpringBoot项目.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cover.png","content":"<h1 id=\"1-上传jar包\"><a href=\"#1-上传jar包\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 上传jar包\"></a>1. 上传jar包</h1><p>将项目打包生成 jar 包或 war 包，将生成的包上传到服务器<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/4e2359816def4e1a814216eb087cf010.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5YehMjIz,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"2-启动项目\"><a href=\"#2-启动项目\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 启动项目\"></a>2. 启动项目</h1><h2 id=\"2-1-终端启动\"><a href=\"#2-1-终端启动\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.1 终端启动\"></a>2.1 终端启动</h2><p>在终端进入 jar 包所在文件夹，执行下面命令</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">java -jar xxxxxxx.jar</code></pre>\n<p>启动项目，使用服务器地址加项目中设置的内置 Tomcat 的端口即可访问。<strong>IP:Port</strong> ，端口需要在防火墙里开放。<br><strong>如：124.222.xxx.90:8001</strong><br>但关闭终端 Tomcat 就停止了，关闭后项目不能再访问。<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/c9ee223987394243aa03376adbfadfe4.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5YehMjIz,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>可以使用下面命令启动</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">nohup java -jar xxxxxx.jar</code></pre>\n<p>表示将该程序在后台一直运行，即使退出终端，项目也可以访问。<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/b88159aaed2f457d98a6660cdff9789d.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5YehMjIz,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>同时会在 jar 包所在目录生成一个 nohup.out 文件，记录运行过程中的信息。<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/a329121e6f8d40b982456885fed8cd7c.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5YehMjIz,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>要关闭项目可以执行下面命令</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">ps -ef | grep 你的进程名称关键字</code></pre>\n<p>显示你的进程相关信息<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/ec21c5a92c2b4a2b96b28c3cc2cc7eff.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5YehMjIz,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>然后使用命令</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">kill -9 进程id</code></pre>\n<p>即可关闭进程，项目停止。<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/18cfd8c045c14bcc9273524e07f2b67d.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5YehMjIz,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"2-2-宝塔面板启动\"><a href=\"#2-2-宝塔面板启动\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.2 宝塔面板启动\"></a>2.2 宝塔面板启动</h2><p>进入网站面板，点击添加 JAVA 项目，选择 SpringBoot 项目类型，然后选择项目 jar 包路径，下面会自动生成，可以设置自己的访问端口。<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/62daa45f55154e529705e25dadf4cb7c.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5YehMjIz,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>可以设置绑定自己的域名<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/573169705d5e49ce9d0f4de2912e2ddc.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5YehMjIz,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>点击提交，项目启动，正常状态运行中。<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/856b06d92f2744699c8c02686341802a.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5YehMjIz,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>使用服务器地址加项目设置的端口即可访问。<strong>IP:Port</strong> ，同样的该端口要在防火墙中开放。假如绑定了域名，直接访问你的域名即可访问。<br><strong>如：124.222.xxx.90:8081 或 xxx.com</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"2-3-报错问题解决\"><a href=\"#2-3-报错问题解决\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.3 报错问题解决\"></a>2.3 报错问题解决</h2><p>1、文件权限问题<br>假如项目有生成输出日志的文件夹，需要对该文件夹及其下的日志文件把用户组和公共都加上写入权限，默认生成的文件夹和文件没有写入权限。项目启动会报日志文件权限错误，启动失败。<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/9b28989c2a38439794f6e689aa6712f9.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5YehMjIz,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>2、端口权限问题<br>项目设置的端口假如在 1000 以下，需要 root 权限，这时启动项目会报 SpringBoot 的内置 Tomcat 启动失败，需要把端口设置成 1000 以上。</p>\n","feature":false,"text":"1. 上传jar包将项目打包生成 jar 包或 war 包，将生成的包上传到服务器 2. 启动项目2.1 终端启动在终端进入 jar 包所在文件夹，执行下面命令 java -jar xxxxxxx.jar 启动项目，使用服务器地址加项目中设置的内置 Tomcat 的端口即可访问。...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":806,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"服务器","slug":"服务器","count":2,"path":"api/categories/服务器.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"服务器","slug":"服务器","count":3,"path":"api/tags/服务器.json"},{"name":"SpringBoot","slug":"SpringBoot","count":1,"path":"api/tags/SpringBoot.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-%E4%B8%8A%E4%BC%A0jar%E5%8C%85\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1. 上传jar包</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2. 启动项目</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-1-%E7%BB%88%E7%AB%AF%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.1 终端启动</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-2-%E5%AE%9D%E5%A1%94%E9%9D%A2%E6%9D%BF%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.2 宝塔面板启动</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-3-%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.3 报错问题解决</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"凡","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Fan223","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"https://weibo.com/u/7318914058","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/tridiamond","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/ACE_U_005A","juejin":"https://juejin.cn/user/1873223546578589","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"电脑软件有网但访问网址显示未连接问题解决","uid":"c1bfd81bf358c0811575f4b1b2b672c7","slug":"电脑软件有网但访问网址显示未连接问题解决","date":"2022-02-10T04:45:04.000Z","updated":"2022-03-14T14:17:18.296Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/电脑软件有网但访问网址显示未连接问题解决.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cover.png","text":"1. 运行 Windows 网络诊断，查看详情 2. 打开控制面板点击网络和 Internet 3. 点击Internet选项 4. 在连接界面点击局域网设置 5. 取消勾选 为 LAN 使用代理服务器确定，保存退出。 ","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":110,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"系统使用","slug":"系统使用","count":2,"path":"api/categories/系统使用.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Windows","slug":"Windows","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Windows.json"}],"author":{"name":"凡","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Fan223","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"https://weibo.com/u/7318914058","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/tridiamond","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/ACE_U_005A","juejin":"https://juejin.cn/user/1873223546578589","customs":{}}},"feature":false},"next_post":{"title":"微服务架构构建","uid":"94a5215fdc37933498533eb05b7ae0a3","slug":"微服务架构构建","date":"2022-02-07T16:09:04.000Z","updated":"2022-03-14T14:17:31.927Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/微服务架构构建.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cover.png","text":"1. 整体聚合父工程1.1 建项目也可以不选 Maven 骨架，直接创建 Maven 项目删除其他多余文件夹 1.2 改父 POM&lt;!-- 打包方式改为 pom --&gt; &lt;packaging&gt;pom&lt;&#x2F;packaging&gt; &lt;!...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.9k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"开发工具环境","slug":"开发工具环境","count":6,"path":"api/categories/开发工具环境.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"微服务","slug":"微服务","count":1,"path":"api/tags/微服务.json"},{"name":"IDEA","slug":"IDEA","count":4,"path":"api/tags/IDEA.json"}],"author":{"name":"凡","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Fan223","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"https://weibo.com/u/7318914058","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/tridiamond","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/ACE_U_005A","juejin":"https://juejin.cn/user/1873223546578589","customs":{}}},"feature":false}}